World distribution. Apart from Balkan also present in Italy (
Foddai et al. 1995
) and North Serbia (Deliblatska Peščara, Fruška Gora Mt.) (
Makarov et al. 2004
).

One of the specimens from the Croatian coastline (
HNHM
) lacks vulvae and gonopods although it is in stadium XII and externally looks like a large adult female, with swollen first leg-pairs; it is here classified as a juvenile.
